      "id": "PopularPost338273",
      "post_content": "I would play this in the same deck as [Fog](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog). Would probably play a 3/1 or 2/2 split.   \n  \nI find it interesting that they actually supplement each other. I think 3/1 with an extra 1 in the side so you can board into a 2/2 split, is the most anyone would want to play unless they are specifically going for the Turbo Fog Deck archetype. Reasons to use Fog tactics but not Turbo Fog strategy exist, but are few.  \n  \nMainly in a Control Deck that chooses to win with something other than [Brain Freeze](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brain Freeze) ",
      "posted_by": "DarthParallax",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost338273\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">I would play this in the same deck as <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fog\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fog\">Fog</a>. Would probably play a 3/1 or 2/2 split. <br/><br/>I find it interesting that they actually supplement each other.  I think 3/1 with an extra 1 in the side so you can board into a 2/2 split, is the most anyone would want to play unless they are specifically going for the Turbo Fog Deck archetype. Reasons to use Fog tactics but not Turbo Fog strategy exist, but are few.<br/><br/>Mainly in a Control Deck that chooses to win with something other than <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Brain Freeze\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Brain Freeze\">Brain Freeze</a> </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '338273'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy46041\">DarthParallax</span>\r\n                                (9/9/2013 12:32:53 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainCo